'''High Prophet''' of the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]] was the title of the [[Supreme Prophet]]'s chief lieutenant, in the cult the [[Prophets of the Dark Side]]. Under the leadership of [[Kadann]], [[Jedgar]] served as High Prophet. After the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]], the [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence]] impersonator of Jedgar usurped the title.

